  <p class="gd-byline" style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:12.5px;letter-spacing:.05em;color:var(--blue-soft);opacity:.9;margin:16px 0 0">By <a href="/about" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px">Vegard Knudsen</a> · Founder, Heliski Travel · Updated 27 May 2026</p>
  <p class="gd-lede">Yes &mdash; a confident intermediate can absolutely go heliskiing, and the belief that you must be an expert is the sport&rsquo;s most persistent myth. If you ski red runs comfortably and link turns off-piste, you qualify. See our <a href="/packages">packages</a> and explore heliskiing in <a href="/iceland">Iceland</a>.</p>
